---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Realty" description="Whitecap Estates is a full-service real estate team serving buyers and sellers across DFW. Local expertise, elevated service, at every price point.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="realty-hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container realty-hero-content">
      <span class="section-label">Whitecap Estates Realty</span>
      <h1>Full-Service Real Estate.<br/>Local Expertise. No Compromises.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Whether you're selling a starter home or a luxury property, we bring the same level of attention, market knowledge, and honest guidance to every transaction.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/9SxML1xwikVAWDfg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
        <a href="#why-whitecap" class="btn btn-outline">Why Whitecap Estates</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY LIST WITH US -->
  <section id="why-whitecap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Why Whitecap Estates</span>
          <h2>We Know This Market Because We've Lived in It</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p>We're not a franchise. We're not a team of agents who relocated here last year. Our team is made up of DFW natives who grew up in Rockwall and McKinney and have spent their careers investing in and selling property across the Metroplex.</p>
          <p>That local depth shows up in the details: accurate pricing, genuine neighborhood knowledge, and a network of buyers, investors, and professionals built over years of doing deals in this market. We know DFW neighborhoods because we've lived and worked in them. We know how to price a property correctly and position it to attract the right offer.</p>
          <p>We operate under Corey Simpson and Associates and bring full brokerage resources to every transaction, backed by the kind of personal attention you only get from a boutique team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-stats">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <strong>500+</strong>
            <span>Transactions across DFW</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <strong>DFW Native</strong>
            <span>Born and raised in the Metroplex</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <strong>Licensed</strong>
            <span>Texas Realtors and active investors</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <strong>Full Service</strong>
            <span>From pricing to closing, we handle it</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DO -->
  <section class="off-white-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="section-label">Our Services</span>
        <h2>Everything You Need to Sell With Confidence</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-num">01</div>
          <h4>Accurate Pricing Strategy</h4>
          <p>We don't pad numbers to win the listing and we don't underprice to move fast. We price based on real market data and give you an honest assessment of what your home will sell for and why.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-num">02</div>
          <h4>Professional Marketing</h4>
          <p>Photography, listing copy, MLS exposure, and targeted outreach to qualified buyers. Your property will be presented at its best to the right audience from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-num">03</div>
          <h4>Negotiation That Protects You</h4>
          <p>We've been on both sides of the table, as agents and as investors. We know how buyers think, how offers are structured, and how to negotiate terms that work in your favor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-num">04</div>
          <h4>Transaction Management</h4>
          <p>From contract to closing, we coordinate inspections, appraisals, title, and every step in between. You'll always know where things stand and what's coming next.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-num">05</div>
          <h4>Vendor Network</h4>
          <p>Need a contractor, stager, photographer, or title company? We have trusted relationships across DFW built through years of doing business here. One call and we'll point you in the right direction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-num">06</div>
          <h4>Investor & Unique Property Experience</h4>
          <p>We've bought and sold investment properties, inherited homes, and non-traditional listings. If your situation doesn't fit the standard playbook, we've likely seen something similar before.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="section-label">The Process</span>
        <h2>What Working With Us Looks Like</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-num">1</div>
          <h4>Consultation</h4>
          <p>We sit down with you, walk the property, and listen. Before we talk numbers, we want to understand your timeline, your goals, and any factors that affect how we approach the sale.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-num">2</div>
          <h4>Pricing & Prep</h4>
          <p>We give you a clear pricing recommendation backed by market data and walk you through anything worth addressing before we go to market without pushing unnecessary repairs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-num">3</div>
          <h4>Go to Market</h4>
          <p>Professional photography, a polished listing, and active outreach to buyers and agents in our network. We don't list and wait we work to generate interest from the first day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-card">
          <div class="process-num">4</div>
          <h4>Negotiate & Close</h4>
          <p>We present every offer with full context, advise you on terms beyond just price, and stay with you through closing to make sure nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DUAL ADVANTAGE -->
  <section class="navy-bg">
    <div class="container dual-inner">
      <div>
        <span class="section-label" style="color: var(--accent-light);">Our Advantage</span>
        <h2>We Can Buy It, List It, or Help You Compare Both</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Most sellers have to choose between a traditional agent and an investor. With Whitecap Estates, you don't. Because we're both licensed Realtors and active buyers, we can show you exactly what a market listing would net versus a direct sale with real numbers, not guesses.</p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">That transparency is rare. Most agents won't tell you when a cash offer makes more sense. Most investors won't tell you when it doesn't. We will.</p>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/9SxML1xwikVAWDfg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 8px;">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
      <div class="dual-options">
        <div class="dual-card">
          <h4>List on the Market</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Full MLS exposure</li>
            <li>Professional marketing</li>
            <li>Competitive offers from multiple buyers</li>
            <li>Typically maximizes sale price</li>
            <li>Best for move-in ready or well-maintained homes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="dual-card">
          <h4>Direct Cash Offer</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>No repairs, no showings</li>
            <li>Fast, flexible closing timeline</li>
            <li>No commissions or fees</li>
            <li>Certainty no financing contingencies</li>
            <li>Best for as-is, inherited, or time-sensitive situations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CASH OFFER SECTION -->
  <section class="off-white-bg">
    <div class="container cash-inner">
      <div class="cash-content">
        <span class="section-label">Need a Different Path?</span>
        <h2>Not Every Property Fits a Traditional Listing</h2>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>If you're dealing with an inherited property, a home that needs significant work, a complicated title situation, or a timeline that doesn't allow for a traditional sale process we can make a direct cash offer.</p>
        <p>No repairs required. No showings. No commissions. We close on your schedule and handle the details so you don't have to.</p>
        <div class="cash-situations">
          <span>Inherited property</span>
          <span>Needs major repairs</span>
          <span>Title complications</span>
          <span>Multiple heirs</span>
          <span>Behind on payments</span>
          <span>Out-of-state owner</span>
          <span>Tenant occupied</span>
          <span>Estate sale</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/9SxML1xwikVAWDfg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 24px; display: inline-block;">Get a Cash Offer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="text-center">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 600px;">
      <span class="section-label">Let's Talk</span>
      <h2>Ready to Find Out What Your Home Is Worth?</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p>Schedule a free consultation. We'll walk the property, run the numbers, and give you an honest picture of your options whether that's listing, a direct offer, or something in between.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions" style="margin-top: 32px;">
        <a href="https://calendar.app.google/9SxML1xwikVAWDfg8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
        <div class="cta-phones">
          <span>Or call directly:</span>
          <a href="tel:4693585646">Kyle: (469) 358-5646</a>
          <a href="tel:9453499179">Cristian: (945) 349-9179</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
/* HERO */
.realty-hero {
  position: relative;
  background: var(--navy);
  padding: 110px 24px 90px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.realty-hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 60%, var(--navy-light) 100%);
}

.realty-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 50%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(200,169,110,0.06), transparent);
}

.realty-hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 700px;
}

.realty-hero h1 {
  color: var(--white);
  margin: 12px 0 20px;
  line-height: 1.15;
}

.hero-sub {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  max-width: 580px;
}

.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* WHY STATS */
.two-col {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: start;
}

.why-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
}

.stat-card {
  background: var(--off-white);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--accent);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  padding: 24px 20px;
}

.stat-card strong {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  color: var(--navy);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.stat-card span {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--gray-text);
  line-height: 1.4;
}

/* SERVICES */
.services-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 48px;
}

.service-card {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  padding: 28px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}

.service-card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,59,92,0.08);
}

.service-num {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--accent);
  opacity: 0.5;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  line-height: 1;
}

.service-card h4 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
.service-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; margin: 0; }

/* PROCESS */
.process-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 0;
  margin-top: 48px;
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.process-card {
  padding: 32px 28px;
  border-right: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  background: var(--white);
}

.process-card:last-child { border-right: none; }

.process-num {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--navy);
  color: var(--white);
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.process-card h4 { margin-bottom: 10px; }
.process-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; }

/* DUAL ADVANTAGE */
.dual-inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
  gap: 64px;
  align-items: center;
}

.dual-options {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
}

.dual-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  padding: 24px 28px;
}

.dual-card h4 {
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.dual-card ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}

.dual-card li {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
  padding-left: 16px;
  position: relative;
}

.dual-card li::before {
  content: '✓';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--accent);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
}

/* CASH OFFER */
.cash-inner {
  max-width: 720px;
}

.cash-situations {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-top: 24px;
}

.cash-situations span {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--navy);
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* FINAL CTA */
.cta-actions {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
}

.cta-phones {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  font-size: 0.92rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
}

.cta-phones span { color: var(--gray-text); }
.cta-phones a { font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); }
.cta-phones a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .process-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .process-card:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
  .process-card:nth-child(1),
  .process-card:nth-child(2) { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); }
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .two-col, .dual-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .why-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .services-grid, .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .process-card { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); }
  .process-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
}
</style>
